{"id":81,"date":"2020-07-16T15:42:54","date_gmt":"2020-07-16T15:42:54","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/enfantcheri.flywheelsites.com\/?page_id=81"},"modified":"2020-07-20T09:32:17","modified_gmt":"2020-07-20T09:32:17","slug":"history","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/","title":{"rendered":"History"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\">Enfant Cheri Study Centre, Inc <\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"430\" height=\"334\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-120\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture1.jpg 430w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture1-300x233.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture1-150x117.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">The idea of putting up a school was conceived by three hardworking teachers: Rose Tampil, Flora Aurea and Nelly Pe\u00f1a. They shared the vision with a retired Public Schools District Supervisor, Mrs. Nila C. Quieta, who helped them turn it into reality.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">A corporation was born out of a commitment forged by five incorporators whose primary objective is to provide quality education to the children of Butuan City and ultimately, to the whole region of Caraga.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"495\" height=\"338\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture2.jpg\" alt=\"Pioneer Class\" class=\"wp-image-125\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture2.jpg 495w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture2-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture2-150x102.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">The school started its operation in 1992 with 88 Nursery, Kindergarten 1 and 2 pupils in Mrs. Quieta\u2019s residence. The number of enrollees grew steadily year after year, which pushed the administrators to expand. A more spacious lot in Purok 1A, Upper Doongan, Butuan City was purchased in 1996.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">The construction of a new school building started in School Year 2003-2004 which has been its permanent home since. Because of its new location, two of the Board of Directors, Nila C. Quieta, and her son, Denilo C. Quieta, voluntarily withdrew their membership from the corporation leaving the three incorporators determined to go on with their endeavors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"729\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4-1024x729.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"128\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/picture4\/\" class=\"wp-image-128\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4-1024x729.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4-768x547.jpg 768w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4-150x107.jpg 150w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture4.jpg 1289w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"743\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5-1024x743.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"129\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/picture5\/\" class=\"wp-image-129\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5-1024x743.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5-300x218.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5-768x557.jpg 768w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5-150x109.jpg 150w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture5.jpg 1260w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"727\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6-1024x727.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"130\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/picture6\/\" class=\"wp-image-130\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6-1024x727.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6-300x213.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6-768x545.jpg 768w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6-150x106.jpg 150w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture6.jpg 1289w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"630\" height=\"422\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"131\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture7.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/picture7\/\" class=\"wp-image-131\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture7.jpg 630w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture7-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture7-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Enfant Cheri at present<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">The school has climbed to excellence in the past years. It has shaped winners in various inter-school contests in the Divisional, Regional, and National Levels. Each pupil carries with them the marks of a true Cherian \u2013 God-fearing, respectful, well-mannered, brilliant, and fluent in speaking in English.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"134\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n\/\" class=\"wp-image-134\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n-150x84.jpg 150w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107302155_2791180751167083_3081295701904122677_n.jpg 1242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"140\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1\/\" class=\"wp-image-140\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1-150x84.jpg 150w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/107554252_282172626337745_2193310061106293589_n-1.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"137\" data-link=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n\/\" class=\"wp-image-137\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n-150x84.jpg 150w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/108634967_750851819058664_5721647378566441217_n.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">In School Year 2010 \u2013 2011, the school branched out to San Francisco, Agusan del Sur. The satellite school bears the same mission-vision, philosophy of education, curriculum, programs, rules and regulations as the mother school. It started with 78 Nursery and Kindergarten pupils and three teachers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture12-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-145\" width=\"301\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture12-1.jpg 722w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture12-1-230x300.jpg 230w, https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/Picture12-1-115x150.jpg 115w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 301px) 100vw, 301px\" \/><figcaption>Enfant Cheri San Francisco, Agusan del Sur<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">Presently, Enfant Cheri continues to soar to greater heights. Adapting to the \u201cnew normal\u201d, it currently offers Modified Home Schooling to its students where they will continue to learn through online classes with trained and equipped teachers who will teach, and with the cooperation of the students\u2019 parents who will provide guidance.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Enfant Cheri Study Centre, Inc The idea of putting up a school was conceived by three hardworking teachers: Rose Tampil, Flora Aurea and Nelly Pe\u00f1a. They shared the vision with<\/br><\/br><a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/history\/\">\u2192  Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-history.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/81"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=81"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/81\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":149,"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/81\/revisions\/149"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/enfantcheri.edu.ph\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=81"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}